1>Go to script runner
2>click on Listeners
3>Click on create Listeners
4>Name -> Create a Subtask based on Priority
5>Applied to -> Select your project
6>Event -> issue created
7>condition -> add the below script
return issue.priority?.name in ['P1-Stopper','P2-High']
8>Target issue type -> Sub-task
9>Field to Copy -> All
10>Additional issue action -> add the below script

import com.atlassian.jira.component.ComponentAccessor

// 1) Assign to the requested user
def u = ComponentAccessor.userManager.getUserByName('ad_rkarekax') ?: ComponentAccessor.userManager.getUserByKey('ad_rkarekax')
issue.setAssignee(u)

// Prefix summary with the parent's Priority label (e.g., "P1-Stopper" or "P2-High")
def prio = sourceIssue.priority?.name ?: ''
issue.setSummary("${prio}: ${sourceIssue.summary}")

11>Click on Add
